name: FAY & DEMY

FAY & DEMY

Similar but different ;

Although FAY and DEMY are different kinds of living things, they share the same specific character; love of beauty, softly gentle, solitary, and peace. Both of them are always watchful not to let anyone harm their body and soul. Therefore they can live in their world peacefully.
